{{Top|leg}}
The '''dweebit''' was a small reddish-brown beetle native to the [[Yuuzhan Vong galaxy]], and brought into [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] by [[Yomin Carr]]. They were installed on the world of [[Belkadan/Legends|Belkadan]], where they emitted extremely noxious fumes, converting the [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] to a mix of [[Carbon dioxide/Legends|carbon dioxide]], [[Methane/Legends|methane]], and [[Sulfur/Legends|sulfur]], killing or mutating all wildlife on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. Yomin Carr considered these dweebits as his pets.

Dweebits were also installed upon [[Tandun III]], where, along with untold numbers of other Vong [[biot]]s, they contributed to the planet's eventual destruction due to unchecked activity.

